'''飓风布伦达'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Brenda}}）是有纪录以来第一个[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]墨西哥[[坎佩切州|坎佩切州]]的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="ATCR">{{cite web | author1 = Paul J. Herbert | author2 = Neil L. Frank | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 1974-01-28 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1973 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1973.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191753/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1973.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，源自1973年8月9日离开非洲西岸、并且穿越大西洋期间基本没有发展的[[东风波|东风波]]。8月18日，东风波关联的[[低气压|低气压区]]已经发展出足够[[对流|对流]]，成为热带低气压。系统当天就增强成热带风暴，然后进入[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]上空。8月21日，布伦达已回到海上并开始快速强化，还在当天形成[[风眼|风眼]]。气旋达到的[[最大持续风速|最高持续风速]]为每小时140公里，接近一级飓风标准上限，然后登陆坎佩切州。风暴进入陆地上空后迅速减弱，最终于次日消散。

布伦达先后两次登陆墨西哥，第一次是尤卡坦半岛，第二次是坎佩切州。尤卡坦半岛遭受的破坏程度很轻，但坎佩切州灾情严重。整场飓风共导致十人死亡，超过2000人无家可归，气旋在部分地区引发的洪灾严重程度创下25年新高。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Brenda 1973 track.png}}
8月9日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西岸进入大西洋，起初呈快速减弱趋势。但到了8月13日，东风波已在途经[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]期间开始再生，产生零散的[[对流|对流]]活动。数天后，系统关联的对流聚拢成中心，经过充分组织而在8月18日成为热带低气压。<ref name="ATCR" /><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Specialists Unit | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Easy to Read HURDAT 1851-2008 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031132/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html }}</ref>次日清晨，系统附近多艘船只测得烈风强度风速，气象机构因此把气旋升级成热带风暴并用“布伦达”（{{lang|en|Brenda}}）命名。风暴在首度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]前快速强化，中心[[气压|气压]]降至992[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.29[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），<ref name="ATCR" />风速达到每小时105公里<ref name="HURDAT" />。系统向内陆行进，于8月19日抵达[[科苏梅尔岛|科苏梅尔岛]]以北约48公里的[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]北部边缘<ref name="ATCR" />。

登陆约24小时后，布伦达的中心直接从墨西哥[[梅里达_(墨西哥)|梅里达]]上空经过。受[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]南部和墨西哥北部上空的强劲[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，气旋出人意料地转向西南。8月20日下午，风暴中心进入[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]。<ref name="ATCR" />系统回到海上后开始快速强化，当晚就达到飓风标准<ref name="HURDAT" />。次日，气旋发展出层次分明的[[风速|风速]]，达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]140公里、最低气压977毫巴（百帕，28.85英寸汞柱）的最高强度，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下接近一级飓风上限<ref name="ATCR" /><ref name="HURDAT" />。与此同时，布伦达的热带风暴强度风场从中心向北延伸240公里、向南延伸121公里<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1973-08-21 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Hurricane Brenda Whirls Southwest | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BMANAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3505,10926&dq=hurricane+brenda | archive-date = 2021-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210812032519/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BMANAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3505%2C10926&dq=hurricane+brenda }}</ref>。当天，风暴就以最高强度从墨西哥[[卡门城|卡门城]]附近登陆，成为有纪录以来首场直接袭击坎佩切州的飓风。气旋进入陆地上空后迅速减弱，于8月22日早上降级成热带低气压，并于当天消散。<ref name="ATCR" />

== 影响和善后 ==
催生飓风布伦达的东风波发展期间在[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]产生可观雨量，[[大开曼|大开曼]]8月17日测得100毫米降水<ref name="ATCR" />。从尤卡坦半岛北部登陆后，风暴产生狂风暴雨<ref name="SPT2">{{cite news | author = United Press International | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1973-08-22 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Brenda Slashes Into Mexico; 2 Persons Killed | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BcANAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6895,624077&dq=hurricane+brenda | archive-date = 2021-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210812032437/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BcANAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6895%2C624077&dq=hurricane+brenda }}</ref>，阵风时速接近110公里。海岸沿线出现6.1米的巨浪<ref name="ATCR" />。一艘载有25人的货轮遭遇风暴后发动机失灵，被困在海上<ref name="SPT1">{{cite news | agency = United Press International | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1973-08-22 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Brenda Sloshes Into Mexico; 2 Persons Killed | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BcANAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6895,624077&dq=hurricane+brenda+1973 | archive-date = 2021-11-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211119042026/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BcANAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6895%2C624077&dq=hurricane+brenda+1973 }}</ref>。8月21日气旋进入墨西哥湾后，接到货轮求救信号的[[美国海岸警卫队|美国海岸警卫队]]开展救援<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = The Free-Lance Star | date = 1973-08-21 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Hurricane drifting off coast of Mexico | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=rmoQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3YsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=7389,2536951&dq=hurricane+brenda | archive-date = 2021-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210812031111/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=rmoQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3YsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=7389%2C2536951&dq=hurricane+brenda }}</ref>。

墨西哥此前已经受到严重洪灾摧残，导致至少18人死亡，20万人流离失所，布伦达来袭后降下瓢泼大雨并引发洪灾，令灾情雪上加霜<ref name="ATCR" /><ref name="LAT1">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1973-08-20 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Hurricane Brenda Heightens Flooding Misery in Mexico | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/157347995.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2020,%201973&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=Hurricane%20Brenda%20Heightens%20Flooding%20Misery%20in%20Mexico | archive-date = 2017-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171216144054/https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/157347995.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2020,%201973&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=Hurricane%20Brenda%20Heightens%20Flooding%20Misery%20in%20Mexico | dead-url = no }}</ref>。飓风过去后，该国又遭遇重大[[地震|地震]]，大量建筑倒塌，救灾工作受阻<ref>{{cite news | author = Francis B. Kent | publisher = [[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 1973-08-30 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Torrential Rains Hamper Hunt for Quake Victims in Mexico | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/157315437.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2030,%201973&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=Torrential%20Rains%20Hamper%20Hunt%20for%20Quake%20Victims%20in%20Mexico | archive-date = 2017-12-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171217014032/https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/157315437.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2030,%201973&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=Torrential%20Rains%20Hamper%20Hunt%20for%20Quake%20Victims%20in%20Mexico | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴期间，陆地上的阵风时速高达180公里，造成严重破坏<ref name="LAT1" /><ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Pittsburgh Post-Gazette | date = 1973-08-29 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Nearly 500 Die in Mexico Quake | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BksNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Dm0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6079,3674459&dq=hurricane+brenda | archive-date = 2021-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210812032450/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BksNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Dm0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6079%2C3674459&dq=hurricane+brenda }}</ref>。整场飓风共夺走十条人命<ref name="ATCR" />，[[坎佩切|坎佩切]]约八成城区被淹，且有两人丧生<ref name="SPT1" />。沿海城市[[韦拉克鲁斯_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|韦拉克鲁斯]]遭遇25年间最严重的洪灾<ref name="ATCR" />，导致两人遇难<ref name="SPT2" />。据官员透露，墨西哥共有452户民居或地方码头被毁<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | publisher = Grupo Editorial Milenio | date = 2009-08-22 | accessdate = 2011-10-05 | title = A 36 años, recuerdan la furia de "Brenda" | url = http://impreso.milenio.com/node/8628715 | archivedate = 2011-10-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111005215710/http://impreso.milenio.com/node/8628715 }}</ref>。受气旋直接影响，该国估计有2000人无家可归<ref name="ATCR" />。

